# Per-device secret configs — copy from config.example.* and keep local.
# (Defaults are committed with placeholder values so `pio run` works out of the
# box; if you put real Wi-Fi/secret material in these, they stay untracked.)
**/config.h
cam-k230/config.py
cam-pi/cam-pi.json

# PlatformIO / CMake build output
**/.pio/
**/build/

# Python bytecode (CanMV host syntax-checks)
**/__pycache__/
